# ============================================================
# Summary: Standard .NET / Visual Studio / Docker ignores.
# Ensures build artifacts, user secrets, and IDE files never
# enter version control – critical for security (no secrets).
# ============================================================

## .NET Build & Output
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
*.user
*.suo
*.cache
*.log

## Visual Studio & Rider
.vs/
.idea/
*.swp
*.sln.docstates

## NuGet packages (do not commit actual packages)
**/packages/*
!**/packages/repositories.config

## EF Core Migrations (generated files tracked by team)
# Do NOT ignore Migrations folder, it's part of the schema.

## Secrets – NEVER COMMIT (ADR-031)
appsettings.*.json
!appsettings.json
!appsettings.Development.json
!appsettings.Testing.json
!appsettings.Staging.json
!appsettings.Production.json

## User secrets file (individual dev)
secrets.json

## Docker & Environment
.env
*.env
docker-compose.override.yml

## OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db